---
import SlideBase from "../../layouts/SlideBase.astro";
---

<SlideBase title="KYDE — Seed Round 2026">
  <style slot="head">
    :root {
      --bg:  #f5f4f0;
      --bg1: #eceae4;
      --bd:  #d8d7d1;
      --bd2: #b8b7b0;
      --z3:  #111110;
      --z4:  #242420;
      --z5:  #56554e;
      --z6:  #8a8980;
      --am:  #e04520;
      --wh:  #0a0a09;
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { background: var(--bg); }
    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--z3);
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .slides {
      height: 100vh;
      overflow-y: scroll;
      scroll-snap-type: y mandatory;
      scrollbar-width: none;
      -ms-overflow-style: none;
    }
    .slides::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }

    .slide {
      height: 100vh;
      scroll-snap-align: start;
      scroll-snap-stop: always;
      position: relative;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      padding: 48px 80px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--bd);
    }

    .has-grid::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 48px 48px;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    /* Nav dots */
    .nav-dots {
      position: fixed; right: 18px; top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px;
      z-index: 200;
    }
    .nd {
      width: 3px; height: 3px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--bd2); cursor: pointer;
      transition: height .25s, border-radius .25s, background .25s;
    }
    .nd.on { height: 16px; border-radius: 2px; background: var(--am); }

    .counter {
      position: fixed; bottom: 22px; right: 36px;
      font-family: ui-monospace, monospace;
      font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.22em; color: var(--bd2); z-index: 200;
    }

    .sn {
      position: absolute; top: 48px; right: 80px;
      font-family: ui-monospace, monospace;
      font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.2em; color: var(--bd2);
    }

    /* Label row */
    .lrow { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 32px; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .lrow::after { content:''; flex:1; height:1px; background:var(--bd); }
    .lbl { font-family: ui-monospace, monospace; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--z6); }
    .dp  { width:6px; height:6px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--am); opacity:.8; flex-shrink:0; animation:pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite; }
    @keyframes pulse { 0%,100%{opacity:.3} 50%{opacity:.9} }

    /* Typography */
    .t-hero { font-family:'Inter',sans-serif; font-size:clamp(56px,8.5vw,112px); font-weight:600; letter-spacing:-.03em; line-height:1.06; text-transform:uppercase; color: var(--wh); }
    .t-h1   { font-family:'Inter',sans-serif; font-size:clamp(34px,4.2vw,62px);  font-weight:600; letter-spacing:-.03em; line-height:1.05; color: var(--wh); }
    .t-h2   { font-family:'Inter',sans-serif; font-size:clamp(22px,2.6vw,38px);  font-weight:500; letter-spacing:-.02em; line-height:1.1; color: var(--z3); }
    .t-b    { font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--z4); }
    .t-sm   { font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--z5); }
    .mono   { font-family: ui-monospace, monospace; }
    .am     { color: var(--am); }
    .wh     { color: var(--wh); }
    .dim    { color: var(--z5); }

    /* Cards */
    .card   { border:1px solid var(--bd);  background:var(--bg1); padding:24px 28px; }
    .card-l { border:1px solid var(--bd2); background:var(--bg1); padding:24px 28px; border-left:2px solid var(--am); }

    /* Grids */
    .g3 { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr; gap:1px; background:var(--bd); }
    .g3>* { background:var(--bg); }
    .g2 { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:1px; background:var(--bd); }
    .g2>* { background:var(--bg); }

    /* Stacked rows */
    .rows { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:1px; background:var(--bd); }
    .row  { background:var(--bg); display:grid; grid-template-columns:200px 1fr; gap:24px; padding:24px 28px; align-items:start; flex:1; }

    /* Question rows */
    .qrow { display:grid; grid-template-columns:240px 1fr; gap:24px; padding:22px 28px; background:var(--bg); align-items:start; border-bottom:1px solid var(--bd); }
    .qrow:last-child { border-bottom:none; }

    /* Market numbers */
    .mnum { font-size:clamp(40px,5vw,72px); font-weight:600; letter-spacing:-.03em; color:var(--wh); line-height:1; margin-bottom:10px; }
  </style>

  <!-- Nav dots (11) -->
  <div class="nav-dots">
    <div class="nd on" onclick="gts(0)"></div>
    <div class="nd" onclick="gts(1)"></div>
    <div class="nd" onclick="gts(2)"></div>
    <div class="nd" onclick="gts(3)"></div>
    <div class="nd" onclick="gts(4)"></div>
    <div class="nd" onclick="gts(5)"></div>
    <div class="nd" onclick="gts(6)"></div>
    <div class="nd" onclick="gts(7)"></div>
    <div class="nd" onclick="gts(8)"></div>
    <div class="nd" onclick="gts(9)"></div>
    <div class="nd" onclick="gts(10)"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="counter"><span id="cn">01</span> / 11</div>

  <div class="slides" id="sl">

    <!-- 01 COVER -->
    <section class="slide has-grid">
      <span class="sn">01 / 11</span>
      <div class="lrow"><span class="dp"></span><span class="lbl">KYDE · SEED ROUND 2026</span></div>

      <div style="flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center">
        <p class="mono am" style="font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.3em;margin-bottom:24px">KYDE</p>
        <h1 class="t-hero" style="margin-bottom:32px">
          The Trust &amp; Control Layer<br>for the Agentic Economy.
        </h1>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap">
          <span class="mono" style="font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.12em;color:var(--z5);border:1px solid var(--bd);padding:6px 14px;">EU AI Act</span>
          <span class="mono" style="font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.12em;color:var(--z5);border:1px solid var(--bd);padding:6px 14px;">NIS-2</span>
          <span class="mono" style="font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.12em;color:var(--z5);border:1px solid var(--bd);padding:6px 14px;">DORA</span>
          <span class="mono" style="font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.12em;color:var(--z5);border:1px solid var(--bd);padding:6px 14px;">GDPR</span>
          <span class="mono am" style="font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.12em;border:1px solid rgba(224,69,32,.3);padding:6px 14px;">Audit-Ready from Day One.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding-top:20px;border-top:1px solid var(--bd)">
        <div style="display:flex;gap:48px">
          <div>
            <p class="lbl" style="margin-bottom:6px">STATUS</p>
            <p class="mono am" style="font-size:13px;letter-spacing:.1em">SEED ROUND OPEN</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="lbl" style="margin-bottom:6px">TARGET</p>
            <p class="mono wh" style="font-size:13px;letter-spacing:.1em">€1.6M</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px">
          <p class="mono" style="font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.12em;color:var(--z5)">KYDE.COM</p>
          <p class="lbl" style="color:var(--bd2)">CONFIDENTIAL</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 02 THE PARADIGM SHIFT -->
    <section class="slide">
      <span class="sn">02 / 11</span>
      <div class="lrow"><span class="lbl">↳ THE PARADIGM SHIFT · 01 / 10</span></div>

      <h2 class="t-h1" style="margin-bottom:8px;max-width:900px">The era of prompt engineering is over.<br>The era of agent governance has begun.</h2>
      <p class="t-b dim" style="margin-bottom:24px;flex-shrink:0;max-width:820px">Legacy AI built workspaces for humans. We are building the infrastructure for a world without humans in the loop.</p>

      <div style="flex:1;display:flex;gap:1px;background:var(--bd)">
        <div style="flex:1.4;background:var(--bg);padding:28px 32px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;">
          <p class="lbl mono" style="color:var(--z6);margin-bottom:20px">WORKFORCE COMPOSITION OVER TIME</p>
          <div style="flex:1;position:relative;">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 400 200" preserveAspectRatio="none" style="width:100%;height:100%;">
              <line x1="0" y1="50"  x2="400" y2="50"  stroke="#d8d7d1" stroke-width="1"/>
              <line x1="0" y1="100" x2="400" y2="100" stroke="#d8d7d1" stroke-width="1"/>
              <line x1="0" y1="150" x2="400" y2="150" stroke="#d8d7d1" stroke-width="1"/>
              <polyline points="0,120 80,118 160,117 240,118 320,120 400,122"
                fill="none" stroke="#b8b7b0" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="6,4"/>
              <polyline points="0,185 60,180 120,168 180,148 240,118 300,78 360,32 400,8"
                fill="none" stroke="#e04520" stroke-width="2.5"/>
              <text x="410" y="125" fill="#b8b7b0" font-family="monospace" font-size="9" dominant-baseline="middle">HUMANS</text>
              <text x="410" y="12"  fill="#e04520" font-family="monospace" font-size="9" dominant-baseline="middle">AI AGENTS</text>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:24px;margin-top:12px">
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px">
              <div style="width:20px;height:2px;background:var(--bd2);border-top:2px dashed var(--bd2);"></div>
              <span class="mono" style="font-size:10px;color:var(--z6)">Human Workforce</span>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px">
              <div style="width:20px;height:2px;background:var(--am);"></div>
              <span class="mono" style="font-size:10px;color:var(--am)">Autonomous Agents</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="flex:1;background:var(--bg);padding:32px 36px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:24px;">
          <div>
            <p class="mono am" style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.2em;margin-bottom:10px">RSAC 2026 CONSENSUS</p>
            <p class="t-b" style="font-style:italic;color:var(--z3)">"The industry just realized that autonomous agents act like digital employees, but we secure them like basic software."</p>
          </div>
          <div style="height:1px;background:var(--bd);"></div>
          <div>
            <p class="mono" style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.2em;color:var(--z5);margin-bottom:10px">THE SHIFT</p>
            <p class="t-b">Agents don't need UIs, they don't wait for human permission, and they execute at machine speed.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="height:1px;background:var(--bd);"></div>
          <div>
            <p class="mono" style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.2em;color:var(--z5);margin-bottom:10px">THE GAP</p>
            <p class="t-b">The enterprise lacks the operational <strong class="wh">System of Record</strong> to govern a workforce that operates entirely via APIs and MCPs.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 03 THE ENTERPRISE LIABILITY GAP -->
    <section class="slide">
      <span class="sn">03 / 11</span>
      <div class="lrow"><span class="lbl">↳ THE ENTERPRISE LIABILITY GAP · 02 / 10</span></div>

      <h2 class="t-h1" style="margin-bottom:8px;max-width:860px">Moving to multi-tenant production<br>breaks legacy IAM.</h2>
      <p class="t-b dim" style="margin-bottom:24px;flex-shrink:0;max-width:820px">Agents amplify existing risks while creating massive new blind spots. Enterprises cannot answer three critical questions:</p>

      <div style="flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1px;background:var(--bd)">
        <div class="qrow">
          <div>
            <p class="mono am" style="font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.14em;margin-bottom:4px">IDENTITY HIJACKING</p>
            <p class="mono" style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.1em;color:var(--z6)">We don't know who is acting.</p>
          </div>
          <p class="t-b">Agents share global service accounts. No traceable roles or accountability. When something goes wrong, attribution is impossible.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="qrow">
          <div>
            <p class="mono" style="font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.14em;color:var(--z4);margin-bottom:4px">OVER-PERMISSIONING</p>
            <p class="mono" style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.1em;color:var(--z6)">Intern-level access, enterprise-level risk.</p>
          </div>
          <p class="t-b">A research agent has the exact same API access as a critical finance agent. Token budgets explode. Databases are exposed. No scope boundaries enforced.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="qrow" style="border-left:2px solid rgba(224,69,32,.25)">
          <div>
            <p class="mono" style="font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.14em;color:var(--z5);margin-bottom:4px">TAMPER-EVIDENCE</p>
            <p class="mono" style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.1em;color:var(--z6)">Logs that fail in court.</p>
          </div>
          <p class="t-b">Self-reported, vendor-provided logs that <strong class="wh">fail the EU AI Act</strong> and fail in court. A compromised agent can simply rewrite its own log.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 04 THE SOLUTION -->
    <section class="slide">
      <span class="sn">04 / 11</span>
      <div class="lrow"><span class="lbl">↳ THE SOLUTION · 03 / 10</span></div>

      <h2 class="t-h1" style="margin-bottom:8px">From Observation to<br>Deterministic Enforcement.</h2>
      <p class="t-b dim" style="margin-bottom:28px;flex-shrink:0;max-width:820px">Developers build the Agent Core. KYDE provides the Multi-Tenant Firewall. We translate chaotic deployments into governed, accountable infrastructure.</p>

      <div style="flex:1;display:flex;gap:1px;background:var(--bd)">
        <div style="flex:1;background:var(--bg);padding:32px 36px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center">
          <p class="mono" style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.2em;color:var(--z6);margin-bottom:20px">ARCHITECTURE</p>
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1px;margin-bottom:24px">
            <div style="background:var(--bg1);border:1px solid var(--bd);padding:16px 20px;">
              <p class="mono" style="font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.12em;color:var(--z5)">YOUR AGENT FLEET</p>
              <p class="t-sm" style="margin-top:4px">Custom enterprise agents, MCP clients, external integrations</p>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;height:28px;">
              <div style="width:1px;height:28px;background:var(--am);opacity:.5;"></div>
            </div>
            <div style="background:var(--bg1);border:1px solid rgba(224,69,32,.3);border-left:2px solid var(--am);padding:16px 20px;">
              <p class="mono am" style="font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.12em;">KYDE WITNESS — MULTI-TENANT FIREWALL</p>
              <p class="t-sm" style="margin-top:4px">Identity · Role Mapping · Budget · Signing · Ledger</p>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;height:28px;">
              <div style="width:1px;height:28px;background:var(--bd2);opacity:.5;"></div>
            </div>
            <div style="background:var(--bg1);border:1px solid var(--bd);padding:16px 20px;">
              <p class="mono" style="font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.12em;color:var(--z5)">ANY LLM PROVIDER</p>
              <p class="t-sm" style="margin-top:4px">OpenAI · Anthropic · Gemini · Mistral · self-hosted</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="flex:1;background:var(--bg);padding:32px 36px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:22px">
          <p class="mono" style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.2em;color:var(--z6)">THREE ENFORCEMENT PILLARS</p>
          <div style="height:1px;background:var(--bd);"></div>
          <div>
            <p class="mono am" style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.2em;margin-bottom:8px">↳ BEHAVIORAL ROLE MAPPING</p>
            <p class="t-b">We translate chaotic agent deployments into standard behavioral profiles — Observer, Executor, Orchestrator. Every agent knows exactly what it is permitted to be.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="mono" style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.2em;color:var(--z4);margin-bottom:8px">↳ LIABILITY FIREBREAKS</p>
            <p class="t-b">Real-time (&lt;100ms) structural enforcement. Strict API/Tool boundaries, Token-Limits, and Time-Windows — enforced outside the agent's process.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="mono" style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.2em;color:var(--z4);margin-bottom:8px">↳ TAMPER-EVIDENT LEDGER</p>
            <p class="t-b">Every transaction SHA-256 hash-chained. Mathematically proven chain of evidence for BaFin, DORA, and EU AI Act compliance.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 05 ARCHITECTURE / THE WEDGE -->
    <section class="slide has-grid">
      <span class="sn">05 / 11</span>
      <div class="lrow"><span class="lbl">↳ ARCHITECTURE · ZERO-FRICTION WEDGE · 04 / 10</span></div>

      <h2 class="t-h1" style="margin-bottom:8px">Governance without developer pushback.</h2>
      <p class="t-b dim" style="margin-bottom:32px;flex-shrink:0">KYDE sits as an application-layer proxy. One environment variable. The entire fleet is instantly governed.</p>

      <div style="flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:20px">
        <div style="background:#111110;border:1px solid var(--bd);padding:32px 40px;flex-shrink:0">
          <p class="mono" style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.15em;color:#71717a;margin-bottom:16px">DEPLOY IN 30 SECONDS</p>
          <p class="mono" style="font-size:clamp(16px,2vw,26px);letter-spacing:.04em;line-height:1.8;color:#f4f4f5">$ export OPENAI_BASE_URL=https://witness.intranet/v1</p>
          <p class="mono" style="font-size:14px;color:#52525b;margin-top:12px"># Zero SDKs. No code refactoring. Agent sees no difference.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="g3" style="flex:1">
          <div style="padding:28px 30px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center">
            <p class="mono am" style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.2em;margin-bottom:14px">↳ CISO WINS</p>
            <p class="t-b" style="font-size:18px">Instant visibility and control over the "Shadow AI" fleet. You have 47 uncontrolled agents — now you govern all of them.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="padding:28px 30px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center">
            <p class="mono" style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.2em;color:var(--z4);margin-bottom:14px">↳ DEVELOPER WINS</p>
            <p class="t-b" style="font-size:18px;">Provider-agnostic. Switch LLMs instantly. Zero refactoring. Governance stays intact across every model change.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="padding:28px 30px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center">
            <p class="mono" style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.2em;color:var(--z4);margin-bottom:14px">↳ COMPLIANCE WINS</p>
            <p class="t-b" style="font-size:18px">Audit trail active from day one. EU AI Act, DORA, NIS-2 coverage from the moment the proxy is up.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 06 COMPETITIVE LANDSCAPE -->
    <section class="slide">
      <span class="sn">06 / 11</span>
      <div class="lrow"><span class="lbl">↳ COMPETITIVE LANDSCAPE · 05 / 10</span></div>

      <h2 class="t-h1" style="margin-bottom:8px">We are the lock on the vault,<br>not the security camera.</h2>
      <p class="t-b dim" style="margin-bottom:24px;flex-shrink:0;max-width:820px">Every competitor watches agents after the fact. KYDE governs them deterministically before the action lands.</p>

      <div style="flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1px;background:var(--bd)">
        <div class="qrow">
          <div>
            <p class="mono" style="font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.14em;color:var(--z5);margin-bottom:4px">BEHAVIORAL ANALYTICS</p>
            <p class="mono" style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.1em;color:var(--z6)">e.g. Geordie AI</p>
          </div>
          <p class="t-b">They observe agent behavior <em>after the fact.</em> But when an agent drains an API budget at machine speed, watching is too late. Post-hoc visibility is not control.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="qrow">
          <div>
            <p class="mono" style="font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.14em;color:var(--z5);margin-bottom:4px">SEMANTIC FILTERS</p>
            <p class="mono" style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.1em;color:var(--z6)">e.g. Alinia AI</p>
          </div>
          <p class="t-b">They use expensive LLMs to read text payloads. Too slow and too costly for real-time M2M transactions. A stochastic defense against a deterministic threat.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="qrow">
          <div>
            <p class="mono" style="font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.14em;color:var(--z5);margin-bottom:4px">LEGACY GATEWAYS</p>
            <p class="mono" style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.1em;color:var(--z6)">MuleSoft, Cisco</p>
          </div>
          <p class="t-b">Blind to agent context, behavioral roles, and token budgets. Built for human-facing services. Cannot enforce scope boundaries that don't exist in their data model.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="qrow" style="border-left:2px solid rgba(224,69,32,.35)">
          <div>
            <p class="mono am" style="font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.14em;margin-bottom:4px">KYDE'S EDGE</p>
            <p class="mono" style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.1em;color:var(--z6)">Deterministic. Network layer.</p>
          </div>
          <p class="t-b">We block unauthorized tools and budgets <strong class="wh">at the network layer, in milliseconds.</strong> Not probabilistic classification. Hard enforcement. The policy layer cannot be reasoned with.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 07 GO-TO-MARKET -->
    <section class="slide">
      <span class="sn">07 / 11</span>
      <div class="lrow"><span class="lbl">↳ GO-TO-MARKET · THE TROJAN HORSE · 06 / 10</span></div>

